    <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-ink-100/80 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-3 text-sm text-ink-500">
      <p>© 2026 QRtime.ch · Hébergé chez <a href="https://alpivault.ch" class="text-ink-700 hover:text-ink-900 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-ink-200">AlpiVault</a></p>
      <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5">Fait en Suisse <span class="inline-block w-3.5 h-3.5 rounded-sm bg-swiss relative"><span class="absolute inset-0 m-auto w-[1.5px] h-2 bg-white"></span><span class="absolute inset-0 m-auto w-2 h-[1.5px] bg-white"></span></span></p>
    </div>
